    <item>
      <title>裕信银行在搬迁前向德国商业银行发出意向</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-flagged-commerzbank-interest-to-germany-ahead-of-move</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本月初，在德国政府开始出售所持德国商业银行股份之前，裕信银行曾与德国官员商谈入股德国商业银行一事，这进一步加剧了人们对德国政府立场的困惑，因为德国政府并不知道裕信银行将采取这一举措。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/unicredit-flagged-commerzbank-interest-to-germany-ahead-of-move</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 13:24:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>前 NFL 后卫与泰德·克鲁兹竞争参议员席位，但胜算不大，成为德克萨斯州参议院焦点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ex-nfl-linebacker-s-long-shot-bid-against-ted-cruz-emerges-as-texas-nailbiter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三十年来，德克萨斯州民主党一直在努力争取全州职位，但都以失败告终。美国众议员科林·奥尔雷德曾是国家橄榄球联盟的后卫，他想证明这一次的情况有所不同。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/ex-nfl-linebacker-s-long-shot-bid-against-ted-cruz-emerges-as-texas-nailbiter</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯准备招募犯罪嫌疑人前往乌克兰作战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/russia-poised-to-enlist-criminal-suspects-to-fight-in-ukraine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[俄罗斯议员批准了一项法案，旨在扩大招募更多士兵加入军队，以应对总统弗拉基米尔·普京对乌克兰战争中士兵短缺的问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/russia-poised-to-enlist-criminal-suspects-to-fight-in-ukraine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 12:58:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2020 年以来加拿大人口增长首次放缓</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/population-growth-slows-in-canada-for-first-time-since-2020</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总理贾斯汀·特鲁多的政府削减移民数量，加拿大人口的快速增长正在逐渐减缓。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/population-growth-slows-in-canada-for-first-time-since-2020</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 12:43:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>小特朗普出访东欧争取支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-jr-tours-eastern-europe-to-drum-up-support-for-father</link>
      <description><![CDATA[小唐纳德·特朗普将共和党的竞选信息带到了巴尔干地区，誓言他的父亲将结束俄罗斯在乌克兰的战争——并且特朗普第二次担任总统将给东欧带来“巨大的利益”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/trump-jr-tours-eastern-europe-to-drum-up-support-for-father</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 11:30:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>劳工债务举措为绿色投资计划复兴打开大门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/labour-debt-move-opens-door-to-revival-of-green-investment-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国正在出台的一项放松严格财政规则的计划可能有助于首相基尔·斯塔默重启其雄心勃勃的气候投资计划，并回应那些批评其政府缺乏促进增长的计划的人士。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/labour-debt-move-opens-door-to-revival-of-green-investment-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 11:28:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列在黎巴嫩为伊朗和自己设下陷阱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-09-25/in-lebanon-israel-set-a-trap-for-iran-and-itself</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果战争以以色列三次残酷的占领而告终——占领加沙、约旦河西岸和黎巴嫩南部——那么世界上唯一的犹太国家将无法获得长期安全。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2024-09-25/in-lebanon-israel-set-a-trap-for-iran-and-itself</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 11:19:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>利比亚危机谈判重启，石油封锁已进入第二个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/libyan-crisis-talks-to-resume-as-oil-blockade-nears-second-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由联合国牵头的有关利比亚央行危机的会谈重启，与此同时，破坏性的石油封锁已接近第二个月，导致利比亚这个欧佩克成员国的石油产量大幅下降。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-25/libyan-crisis-talks-to-resume-as-oil-blockade-nears-second-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 25 Sep 2024 09:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
